<exercise checkit-seed="0008" checkit-slug="CC2" checkit-title="Constant-Coefficient Linear Non-Homogeneous First-Order IVPs">
  <statement>
    <p>Explain how to find the particular solution to the given IVP.</p>
    <me>16 \, {y} - 4 \, {y'} = -60 \, e^{\left(4 \, t\right)} \sin\left(5 \, t\right);\qquad y(0)=2</me>
  </statement>
  <answer>
    <me>y=-3 \, \cos\left(5 \, t\right) e^{\left(4 \, t\right)} + 5 \, e^{\left(4 \, t\right)}</me>
  </answer>
</exercise>
